  m_Name: NeighborJournal_19
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 36
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #19 \u2014 Linh m\u1EE5c cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i l\xE0 cha Pedro, linh m\u1EE5c c\u1EE7a nh\xE0 th\u1EDD nh\u1ECF
    gi\u1EEFa th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1. Khi d\u1ECBch b\u1EC7nh b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u,
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xE2n k\xE9o \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE2y tr\xFA \u1EA9n \u2014
    t\xF4i nh\u1EDB c\xF3 gia \u0111\xECnh Zoe, \xF4ng Mathew, v\xE0 v\xE0i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    n\u1EEFa. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n m\u1ED7i \u0111\xEAm. Nh\u01B0ng
    r\u1ED3i Zoe b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u ho s\u1ED1t, r\u1ED3i Mathew c\u0169ng v\u1EADy.
    T\xF4i hi\u1EC3u r\u1ED3i \u2014 nh\xE0 th\u1EDD kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7
    ai. T\xF4i ph\u1EA3i b\u1ECF h\u1ECD l\u1EA1i, b\u1ECF Ch\xFAa l\u1EA1i, \u0111\u1EC3
    t\u1EF1 c\u1EE9u m\xECnh. Xin tha th\u1EE9 cho t\xF4i."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
